{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"931366c222","title":"须重视对定海作战的各项问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"df003e7fa1","index":0,"year":1949,"month":11,"day":14,"articleId":"931366c222"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"4948513e00","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"931366c222","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"菜裕，当时任第三野战军兼华东军区副司令员。"},{"id":"1026f10288","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"931366c222","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈、饶，指陈毅、饶激石，当时分别任第三野战军兼华东军区司令员和政治委员。"},{"id":"625d4c26c3","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"931366c222","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1949年10月下句，第三野战军第十兵团一部在缺乏充分渡海作战准备的情况下，仓促发起金门战斗，遭受严重损失。1949年11月3日第三野战军第二十一军第六十一师在攻击定海（即今浙江舟山）登步岛的作战中，对敌据岛顽抗及援军迅速登岛估计不足，遭到敌守军、援军和海空军的联合反击，被迫撤出战斗。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5e08381604","type":"title","text":"须重视对定海作战的各项问题","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"931366c222"},{"id":"4948513e00","type":"paragraph","text":"栗裕\"同志，并告陈、饶”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"931366c222"},{"id":"1026f10288","type":"paragraph","text":"舟山群岛共有敌军五万人，并有频强的战斗力，你们以两个半军进行攻击是否足够？鉴于金门岛及最近定海附近某岛作战的失利，你们须严重注视对定海作战的兵力，部署，准备情况及攻击时机等项问题。如果准备未周，宁可推退时间。提议你们派一要员直赴定海附近巡视检查一次。如何盼复。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"931366c222"},{"id":"625d4c26c3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"931366c222"},{"id":"39b8317fa3","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"931366c222"}],"page":{"id":"6a2dc23745","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"931366c222","start":512,"end":512}}}},"__N_SSG":true}